reviewText: A good little collection of Videos.
Muito Bom, o produto chegou como anunciado, em prefeitas condies, recomendo a todos e voltarei a comprar, muito bom mesmo

This product is a must have only for the real, true, deep and bloody Shakira's fans. It doesn't have never seen materials but only already available videos but collected here in a DVD. It includes even performances from the amazing Mongoose Tour and clips from her last studio albums. If you love Shakira, buy it and it will be not disappoint.
